<p><font size=5>O - 01 Game</font></p>
<p>题目描述<br>    Alica and Bob are playing a game.<br>    Initially they have a binary string s consisting of only characters 0 and 1.<br>    Alice and Bob make alternating moves: Alice makes the first move, Bob makes the second move, Alice makes the third one, and so on.<br>    During each move, the current player must choose two different adjacent characters of string s and delete them. For example, if s=1011001，then the following moves are possible:<br>       delete s1 and s2: 1011001→11001;<br>       delete s2 and s3: 1011001→11001;<br>       delete s4 and s5: 1011001→10101;<br>       delete s6 and s7: 1011001→10110.<br>    If a player can’t make any move, they lose. Both players play optimally.<br>    You have to determine if Alice can win.<br>Input</p>
<pre><code>First line contains one integer t(1≤t≤1000) — the number of test cases.
Only line of each test case contains one string s(1≤|s|≤100), consisting of only characters 0 and 1.</code></pre><p>Output</p>
<pre><code>For each test case print answer in the single line.
If Alice can win print DA (YES in Russian) in any register. 
Otherwise print NET (NO in Russian) in any register.</code></pre><p>Sample Input</p>
<pre><code>3
01
1111
0011</code></pre><p>Sample Output</p>
<pre><code>DA
NET
NET</code></pre><p>Note</p>
<pre><code>In the first test case after Alice&apos;s move string s become empty and Bob can not make any move.
In the second test case Alice can not make any move initially.
In the third test case after Alice&apos;s move string s turn into 01. 
Then, after Bob&apos;s move string s become empty and Alice can not make any move.</code></pre><p>题意</p>
<pre><code>给定一个只含0和1的字符串
Alica(先手)和Bob先后删去字符串中的“01”或“10”到无法删除为止，谁最后无法删除谁输
思维题，01肯定会相遇，所以只需判断01对数再判胜负即可
找规律可得01对数为奇数时Bob必败，反之Alica必败
还有我才搞清c++用&lt;string&gt;!!</code></pre><p>题解代码：</p>
<figure class="highlight c"><figcaption><span>[ 01 Game ]</span></figcaption><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="meta-keyword">include</span><span class="meta-string">&lt;string&gt;//c++用&lt;string&gt;!!!!!!!!!</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="meta-keyword">include</span><span class="meta-string">&lt;iostream&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="meta-keyword">include</span><span class="meta-string">&lt;algorithm&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">using</span> <span class="keyword">namespace</span> <span class="built_in">std</span>;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">int</span> <span class="title">main</span><span class="params">()</span></span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">int</span> t;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="built_in">cin</span>&gt;&gt;t;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">while</span>(t--)&#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="built_in">string</span> s;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="built_in">cin</span>&gt;&gt;s;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">int</span> len=s.length();</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">int</span> s0=<span class="number">0</span>,s1=<span class="number">0</span>;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">for</span>(<span class="keyword">int</span> i=<span class="number">0</span>;i&lt;len;i++)&#123;</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">if</span>(s[i]==<span class="string">'0'</span>)</span><br><span class="line">                s0++;</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">else</span></span><br><span class="line">                s1++;</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">int</span> d=<span class="built_in">min</span>(s0,s1);<span class="comment">//01对数</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">if</span>(d%<span class="number">2</span>==<span class="number">0</span>)<span class="comment">//偶数必败</span></span><br><span class="line">            <span class="built_in">cout</span>&lt;&lt;<span class="string">"NET"</span>&lt;&lt;<span class="built_in">endl</span>;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">else</span></span><br><span class="line">            <span class="built_in">cout</span>&lt;&lt;<span class="string">"DA"</span>&lt;&lt;<span class="built_in">endl</span>;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="number">0</span>;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p><font size=5>P - Game On Leaves</font></p>
<p>题目描述<br>    Ayush and Ashish play a game on an unrooted tree consisting of n nodes numbered 1 to n.<br>    Players make the following move in turns:<br>       Select any leaf node in the tree and remove it together with any edge which has this node as one of its endpoints.<br>    A leaf node is a node with degree less than or equal to 1.<br>    A tree is a connected undirected graph without cycles.<br>    There is a special node numbered x.<br>    The player who removes this node wins the game. Ayush moves first.<br>    Determine the winner of the game if each player plays optimally.<br>Input</p>
<pre><code>The first line of the input contains a single integer t
(1≤t≤10) the number of testcases. 
The description of the test cases follows.
The first line of each testcase contains two integers n and x 
(1≤n≤1000,1≤x≤n) the number of nodes in the tree and the special node respectively.
Each of the next n−1 lines contain two integers u, v 
(1≤u,v≤n, u≠v), meaning that there is an edge between nodes u and v in the tree.</code></pre><p>Output</p>
<pre><code>For every test case, if Ayush wins the game, print &quot;Ayush&quot;, otherwise print &quot;Ashish&quot; (without quotes).</code></pre><p>Sample Input</p>
<pre><code>1
3 1
2 1
3 1</code></pre><p>Sample Output</p>
<pre><code>Ashish</code></pre><p>Sample Input</p>
<pre><code>1
3 2
1 2
1 3</code></pre><p>Sample Output</p>
<pre><code>Ayush</code></pre><p>Note</p>
<pre><code>For the 1st test case
Ayush can only remove node 2 or 3 after which node 1 becomes a leaf node 
And Ashish can remove it in his turn.
For the 2nd test case, Ayush can remove node 2 in the first move itself.</code></pre><p>题意</p>
<pre><code>给定多个只无根树(其实就是无向图吧)
Ayush(先手)和Ashish先后删去树中的叶子结点，谁先删去特殊点X谁赢
思维题
当X为叶子结点或图只有1个结点时Ayush必胜，当不是叶子结点时,看结点数量
摘点时该点度数要为1或0，也就是说要摘得X必须至少要将所有点删至只剩两个点(其中一个是X)
在结点数大于1情况下
找规律可得当n为奇数，后手必胜，反之先手必胜
感觉这都不算什么博弈了(　ﾟ 3ﾟ)</code></pre><p>题解代码：</p>
<figure class="highlight c"><figcaption><span>[ Game On Leaves ]</span></figcaption><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="meta-keyword">include</span><span class="meta-string">&lt;iostream&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="meta-keyword">include</span><span class="meta-string">&lt;string.h&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="meta-keyword">include</span><span class="meta-string">&lt;algorithm&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">using</span> <span class="keyword">namespace</span> <span class="built_in">std</span>;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">int</span> <span class="title">main</span><span class="params">()</span></span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">int</span> t,edg[<span class="number">1001</span>];;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="built_in">cin</span>&gt;&gt;t;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">while</span>(t--)&#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="built_in">memset</span>(edg,<span class="number">0</span>,<span class="keyword">sizeof</span>(edg));</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">int</span> n,x,a,b;;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="built_in">cin</span>&gt;&gt;n&gt;&gt;x;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">for</span>(<span class="keyword">int</span> i=<span class="number">0</span>;i&lt;n<span class="number">-1</span>;i++)&#123;<span class="comment">//算a,b点的度</span></span><br><span class="line">            <span class="built_in">cin</span>&gt;&gt;a&gt;&gt;b;</span><br><span class="line">            edg[a]++;<span class="comment">//度数加一</span></span><br><span class="line">            edg[b]++;</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">if</span>(edg[x]&lt;=<span class="number">1</span>)<span class="comment">//x为叶子结点</span></span><br><span class="line">            <span class="built_in">cout</span>&lt;&lt;<span class="string">"Ayush"</span>&lt;&lt;<span class="built_in">endl</span>;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">else</span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">if</span>(n%<span class="number">2</span>==<span class="number">1</span>)</span><br><span class="line">               <span class="built_in">cout</span>&lt;&lt;<span class="string">"Ashish"</span>&lt;&lt;<span class="built_in">endl</span>;</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">else</span></span><br><span class="line">               <span class="built_in">cout</span>&lt;&lt;<span class="string">"Ayush"</span>&lt;&lt;<span class="built_in">endl</span>;</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="number">0</span>;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

